horization</h2>\n1070 |                     </div>\n1071 |                     \n1072 |                     <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-4 print:border-black/10\">\n1073 |                       <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 leading-snug\">\n1074 |                         By entering your signature below, you endorse the draft SOW outline. This is a secure local simulation of the strategic roadmap setup; no contract data is retained.\n1075 |                       </p>\n1076 | \n1077 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n1078 |                         <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n1079 |                           <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase block\">Authorized Signatory Name</label>\n1080 |                           <input\n1081 |                             type=\"text\"\n1082 |                             value={signName}\n1083 |                             onChange={(e) => setSignName(e.target.value)}\n1084 |                             placeholder=\"e.g. Dr. Catherine Vance\"\n1085 |                             className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded px-3 py-2 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#00FF9D] print:hidden\"\n1086 |                           />\n1087 |                         </div>\n1088 |                         <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n1089 |                           <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase block\">Corporate Title</label>\n1090 |                           <input\n1091 |                             type=\"text\"\n1092 |                             value={signTitle}\n1093 |                             onChange={(e) => setSignTitle(e.target.value)}\n1094 |                             placeholder=\"e.g. VP of Security Compliance\"\n1095 |                             className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded px-3 py-2