lines with zero log leaks.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5 relative overflow-hidden text-left\">\n                          <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-black mb-1.5 uppercase tracking-wide\">DAY 31 - 60</div>\n                          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1\">Agent Fleet Assembly</h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 leading-relaxed font-light mt-1\">\n                            Orchestrate co-innovation agent fleets inside the secure sandbox, wire prompt chains to selected outcomes, and establish user authorization dashboard interfaces.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5 relative overflow-hidden text-left\">\n                          <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-black mb-1.5 uppercase tracking-wide\">DAY 61 - 90</div>\n                          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mb-1\">Federated Go-Live</h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 leading-relaxed font-light mt-1\">\n                            Run stress-testing of low-latency decision loops, perform end-to-end telemetry compliance audit runs, and handover local administrative control keys to client operators.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* SECTION 6: SUGGESTED SQUAD */}\n                  <div id=\"suggested-squad\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n                    <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION VI</span>\n                      <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">👥 Suggested Squad</h2>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n                      <p>\n                        Based on your preferred path, we propose allocating a specialized co-innovation cohort (Cohort: <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold font-mono text-[10px]\">{pData.engagementPathObj.squad}</strong>) optimized for high-security deployment:\n                      </p>\n                      \n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-left\">\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">01 / DEDICATED</span>\n                          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mt-1\">Lead Systems Architect</h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 print:text-black/60 leading-snug font-light mt-1\">\n                            Designs geography boundaries, VPC peering routes, single-tenant clusters, and cryptographic schema filters.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">02 / DEDICATED</span>\n                          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mt-1\">Sovereign Systems Engineer</h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 print:text-black/60 leading-snug font-light mt-1\">\n                            Programs read-only OmniMesh adapters, fine-tunes parameters, compiles container layers, and optimizes loop latency.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[7.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">03 / SHARED COHORT</span>\n                          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black mt-1\">Security Compliance Auditor</h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/40 print:text-black/60 leading-snug font-light mt-1\">\n                            Performs continuous vulnerability scanning and audits zero persistent retention logs on the read-only ledger.\n                          </p>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>"}}}
