2 gap-4 text-left\">\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 space-y-2\">\n                          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">\n                            <span className=\"text-red-400\">⚡</span> Schema Fragmentation Risk\n                          </h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10.5px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 leading-relaxed font-sans font-light\">\n                            Legacy silos inside {pData.org} might contain poorly indexed database schemas, causing query lookup delays.\n                          </p>\n                          <div className=\"pt-2 border-t border-white/5 text-[10px] text-[#00FF9D] font-mono\">\n                            Mitigation: GFF OmniMesh automatically creates a read-only local semantic layer without altering physical tables.\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 space-y-2\">\n                          <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">\n                            <span className=\"text-red-400\">⚡</span> VPC Provisioning Bottlenecks\n                          </h4>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10.5px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70 leading-relaxed font-sans font-light\">\n                            Lead times for single-tenant cloud instance clearance might delay core systems setup.\n                          </p>\n                          <div className=\"pt-2 border-t border-white/5 text-[10px] text-[#00FF9D] font-mono\">\n                            Mitigation: GFF runs lightweight containerized prototypes on isolated local staging nodes immediately, avoiding setup delays.\n       